*bluez-utils-3.11 (24 May 2007)

  24 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +files/3.11/conf.d-hidd, +files/3.11/init.d-hidd,
  +bluez-utils-3.11.ebuild:
